text: (See SOP for Determination of Solubility of Materials for Acute Cardiovascular and Respiratory Effects Study in Beagle Dogs) Reference OR 100-32 .2 mg A30 soluble in .5 mL 10% propylene glycol solution at 38°C. Add A30 to warm (38°C) propylene glycol; add warm water to make 10% propylene glycol solution.
